---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Seasonal Home Maintenance Checklist | HandyHub Blog" description="Keep your home in top shape year-round with this comprehensive seasonal maintenance checklist covering HVAC, plumbing, and more.">
  <Navbar variant="light" />
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- ========== ARTICLE HERO ========== -->
    <section class="article-hero">
      <div class="article-hero__inner container">
        <div class="article-hero__header">
          <span class="section-label">HANDYHUB</span>
          <h1 class="article-hero__heading">Seasonal Home Maintenance Checklist</h1>
          <p class="article-hero__subtext">
            Keep your home in top shape year-round with this comprehensive seasonal maintenance guide covering everything from HVAC to gutters.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="article-hero__image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/blog-detail-hero.jpg"
            alt="Home maintenance tools and materials laid out for a seasonal inspection"
            width="1140"
            height="642"
            class="article-hero__image"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== ARTICLE BODY ========== -->
    <section class="article-body">
      <div class="article-body__inner container">
        <div class="article-body__content">
          <p>
            Home maintenance is an essential part of homeownership that helps protect your investment and keep your living space comfortable and safe. By following a seasonal checklist, you can stay on top of important tasks and avoid costly repairs down the road.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you're a first-time homeowner or have been maintaining your property for years, this guide will help you prioritize the most important tasks for each season.
          </p>

          <h2 class="article-body__subheading">Fixing a Leaky Faucet</h2>
          <p>
            A leaky faucet is one of the most common household problems, and fortunately, it's also one of the easiest to fix. Here's how to tackle it:
          </p>
          <ol class="article-body__list">
            <li><strong>Turn off the water supply</strong> — Locate the shut-off valves under the sink and turn them clockwise to stop the water flow. Turn on the faucet to release any remaining water in the lines.</li>
            <li><strong>Remove the faucet handle</strong> — Use a flathead screwdriver to pry off the decorative cap, then unscrew the handle screw. Gently pull the handle off the stem.</li>
            <li><strong>Replace the washer or cartridge</strong> — Inspect the washer or cartridge for wear and damage. Take the old part to the hardware store to find an exact match, then install the replacement.</li>
            <li><strong>Reassemble and test</strong> — Put the faucet back together in reverse order. Turn the water supply back on and check for leaks. If the drip persists, the valve seat may need replacing.</li>
          </ol>

          <h2 class="article-body__subheading">Patching Small Holes in Drywall</h2>
          <p>
            Small holes in drywall from nails, screws, or minor accidents are easy to repair with a few basic supplies. Here's a step-by-step guide:
          </p>
          <ol class="article-body__list">
            <li><strong>Clean the area</strong> — Remove any loose debris or crumbling drywall around the hole. If there's a nail or screw still in the wall, remove it. Lightly sand the area around the hole for a smooth surface.</li>
            <li><strong>Apply spackling compound</strong> — Using a putty knife, apply a thin layer of spackling compound over the hole. Press firmly to fill the hole completely, then smooth the surface level with the surrounding wall.</li>
            <li><strong>Let it dry and sand</strong> — Allow the spackling compound to dry completely (usually 1-2 hours for small patches). Once dry, sand the area smooth with fine-grit sandpaper (120-150 grit).</li>
            <li><strong>Prime and paint</strong> — Apply a coat of primer to the patched area to ensure even paint coverage. Once the primer dries, paint over the area to match the surrounding wall color.</li>
          </ol>

          <p>
            By staying on top of these common maintenance tasks, you can keep your home in excellent condition and avoid more expensive repairs in the future. Remember, if a project feels beyond your skill level, don't hesitate to call a professional.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== SIMILAR ARTICLES ========== -->
    <section class="similar-articles">
      <div class="similar-articles__inner container">
        <div class="similar-articles__header">
          <span class="section-label">HANDYHUB</span>
          <h2 class="similar-articles__heading">Similar article for you</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="similar-articles__track-wrapper">
          <div class="similar-articles__track">
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-1.jpg" alt="Seasonal home maintenance" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">SEASONAL HOME MAINTENANCE CHECKLIST</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Keep your home in top shape year-round with this comprehensive seasonal maintenance guide.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-2.jpg" alt="Simple DIY fixes" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">SIMPLE FIXES YOU CAN DO YOURSELF</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Save money and time by learning these easy home repairs that any homeowner can handle.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-3.jpg" alt="Budget-friendly DIY improvements" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">BUDGET-FRIENDLY DIY HOME IMPROVEMENTS</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Transform your living space without breaking the bank with these affordable improvement ideas.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-4.jpg" alt="Preventing leaks and clogs" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">PREVENTING LEAKS AND CLOGS</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Learn how to prevent common plumbing issues before they become expensive problems.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-5.jpg" alt="Painting tips" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">PAINTING TIPS FOR A PROFESSIONAL FINISH</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Achieve a flawless paint job with these expert tips on preparation, technique, and finishing.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="similar-card">
              <a href="/blog-detail" class="similar-card__link">
                <div class="similar-card__image-wrapper">
                  <img src="/assets/images/blog-article-6.jpg" alt="Tips before starting a DIY project" width="552" height="320" class="similar-card__image" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="similar-card__body">
                  <h3 class="similar-card__title">TIPS BEFORE STARTING A DIY PROJECT</h3>
                  <p class="similar-card__desc">Essential preparation steps every DIY enthusiast should follow before picking up their tools.</p>
                  <span class="similar-card__cta">LEARN MORE <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="similar-articles__nav">
          <button class="similar-articles__nav-btn similar-articles__nav-btn--prev" aria-label="Previous articles">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="similar-articles__nav-btn similar-articles__nav-btn--next" aria-label="Next articles">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const track = document.querySelector('.similar-articles__track');
    const prevBtn = document.querySelector('.similar-articles__nav-btn--prev');
    const nextBtn = document.querySelector('.similar-articles__nav-btn--next');
    if (!track || !prevBtn || !nextBtn) return;

    const scrollAmount = 560;

    prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      track.scrollBy({ left: -scrollAmount, behavior: 'smooth' });
    });

    nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      track.scrollBy({ left: scrollAmount, behavior: 'smooth' });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* ========== ARTICLE HERO ========== */
  .article-hero {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
    padding-block: 7.5em 3em;
  }

  .article-hero__inner {
    padding-inline: var(--container-padding);
  }

  .article-hero__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3em;
  }

  .article-hero__header .section-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .article-hero__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.75em;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.133;
    letter-spacing: -1.92px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.267em;
  }

  .article-hero__subtext {
    font-size: 0.875em;
    line-height: 1.429;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 40em;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .article-hero__image-wrapper {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .article-hero__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40.125em;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ========== ARTICLE BODY ========== */
  .article-body {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
    padding-block: 3em 7.5em;
  }

  .article-body__inner {
    padding-inline: var(--container-padding);
  }

  .article-body__content {
    max-width: 40em;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .article-body__content p {
    font-size: 1em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  .article-body__subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.5em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.333;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .article-body__list {
    list-style: decimal;
    padding-left: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
  }

  .article-body__list li {
    font-size: 1em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    padding-left: 0.5em;
  }

  .article-body__list li strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  /* ========== SIMILAR ARTICLES ========== */
  .similar-articles {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
    padding-block: 7.5em;
  }

  .similar-articles__inner {
    padding-inline: var(--container-padding);
  }

  .similar-articles__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.75em;
  }

  .similar-articles__header .section-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .similar-articles__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.75em;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.133;
    letter-spacing: -1.92px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .similar-articles__track-wrapper {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .similar-articles__track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25em;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    padding-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .similar-articles__track::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .similar-card {
    flex: 0 0 34.5em;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .similar-card__link {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-base);
  }

  .similar-card__link:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .similar-card__image-wrapper {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .similar-card__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 20em;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .similar-card__body {
    padding: 1.5em;
  }

  .similar-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 1.28px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .similar-card__desc {
    font-size: 0.875em;
    line-height: 1.429;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25em;
  }

  .similar-card__cta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.429;
    letter-spacing: 1.12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .similar-articles__nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1em;
    margin-top: 3em;
  }

  .similar-articles__nav-btn {
    width: 3em;
    height: 3em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    transition: opacity var(--transition-base);
  }

  .similar-articles__nav-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */

  /* Tablet */
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .article-hero__heading {
      font-size: 3em;
    }

    .article-hero__image {
      height: 28em;
    }

    .similar-card {
      flex: 0 0 28em;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .article-hero__heading {
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    .article-hero__image {
      height: 20em;
    }

    .similar-articles__heading {
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }

    .similar-card {
      flex: 0 0 20em;
    }

    .similar-card__image {
      height: 14em;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile portrait */
  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .article-hero__heading {
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    .similar-articles__heading {
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    .similar-card {
      flex: 0 0 85vw;
    }
  }
</style>
